channel.title: Comments on: Nails Inc. Kensington Caviar Base Coat

item.title: By: Erin-Kurley
item.dc:creator: Erin-Kurley
item.description: Definitely going to try this! I thought my Orly free-with-purchase base coat was going to be awesome, but alas, it is total butt. Instead of chipping, the polish just comes off in giant chunks. I normally would just use Sally Hansen somethingorother.
